A young STUDENT (20s, disheveled hair, stressed expression) sits hunched over a laptop, surrounded by scattered textbooks and crumpled papers.

CLOSE ON - LAPTOP SCREEN
A daunting academic assignment brief fills the screen: dense text, complex requirements.

SOUND of frantic keyboard typing, nervous sighs

NARRATOR (V.O.)
