CLOSE ON - SHORESTEP AI INTERFACE
She types in her assignment brief. The AI quickly processes it, then displays a structured output: PRD.md, PLAN.md, TODO.md, PROMPTS.md, and a git-ready folder structure.

SOUND of calm, focused keyboard typing, gentle UI chimes

NARRATOR (V.O.)
Introducing ShoreStep AI. Transform complex assignments into calm, structured action plans.

INT. STUDENT APARTMENT - DAY (45-55 seconds)

